data.description: For sale by owner! Beautiful home located right in the heart of Celestine, IN in highland estates. This 3 bedroom and 4 bath ranch style home has many updated/new features. Completely remodeled basement that features a living area, wet bar, full bathroom, playroom/work out room and large storage space. 2 car attached garage with a 24x24 detached garage as well!! All new concrete in the back/side yard for a basketball goal or RV parking. Large flat backyard with concrete and a new retaining wall (electric ran behind wall for speakers, lights, etc) that makes the backyard very secluded. New AC unit and new garage doors with openers. Just a few miles from Patoka Lake! Contact owners for viewing at 812-865-6318
